attachments.text: With an embedded silicon chip, intelliPaper turns an ordinary strip of paper into a working USB drive.
attachments.fallback: With an embedded silicon chip, intelliPaper turns an ordinary strip of paper into a working USB drive.

text: "The paper used is about as thick as card stock, and the embedded chip can hold 8-32 MB of data – the team has not decided on a fixed capacity yet, but it will be within this range....If someone doesn't want to risk damaging the paper drive itself, intelliPaper also communicates wirelessly with any near field-enabled smartphone or tablet."
